name: Experiment Or Die #38
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. With the recent Skeles crazy and Halloween just behind us I had 1 more spooky design for the season. My wife loves decorating the house for each new holiday and these little guys could be hanging in our kitchen until next year she loves them so much. Halloween is on 24/365 in our house.
